# Student Information System Documentation

## 1. Project Overview

### Project Title

Student Information System

### Objective

The Student Information System is a Java-based console application developed to manage student records efficiently. The project demonstrates the use of Object-Oriented Programming (OOP), ArrayList collections, file handling, input validation, exception handling, and menu-driven user interaction.

The system allows users to:

* Add new student records
* View all student records
* Search students by ID or name
* Update student information
* Delete student records
* Save and load data from a file

This project was developed as a practical exercise to strengthen Java programming skills and understand real-world data management applications.

