## 3. Setup and Installation Instructions

### Prerequisites

* Java Development Kit (JDK 8 or above)
* VS Code, IntelliJ IDEA, Eclipse, or any Java IDE

### Project Structure

StudentInformationSystem/

├── src/

│ ├── Student.java

│ ├── StudentManager.java

│ ├── ValidationUtils.java

│ ├── FileHandler.java

│ └── StudentInformationSystem.java

├── docs/

├── test_data/

└── README.md

### Compilation

Open terminal inside the source folder and run:

javac *.java

### Execution

java StudentInformationSystem

### Data Storage

Student records are automatically stored inside:

students.txt

and loaded whenever the application starts.

